## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="33f59-102">Quando os rótulos inteligentes estão habilitados, o gráfico reposiciona sobrepostos rótulos de ponto de dados, com base em um conjunto de regras definidas pelo usuário.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-102">When smart labels are enabled, the chart repositions overlapping data point labels, based on a set of user-defined rules.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="33f59-103">Linhas de texto explicativo serão desenhadas para vincular o rótulo de ponto de dados.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-103">Callout lines will be drawn to link the label with its data point.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-104">Os atributos visuais de linha de texto explicativo podem ser controlados.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-104">The visual attributes of the callout line can be controlled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-105">Esses atributos visuais incluem cor, estilo de linha e largura da linha.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-105">These visual attributes include color, line style, and line width.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-106">O <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> e <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> propriedades controlam ornamentos, como setas, que aparecem no final da linha do texto explicativo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-106">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> properties control the embellishments, such as arrowheads, that appear at the end of the callout line.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="33f59-107">O <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> propriedade pode ser definida como qualquer <xref:System.Drawing.Color> objeto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-107">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineColor%2A> property can be set to any <xref:System.Drawing.Color> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-108">Se você definir a cor da linha do texto explicativo, você definirá a cor do também automaticamente a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> e o ornamentos definido pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-108">If you set the color of the callout line, you will also automatically set the color of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the embellishment defined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="33f59-109">O <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> propriedade controla a largura de pixel de linha de texto explicativo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-109">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineWidth%2A> property controls the pixel width of the callout line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-110">Uso dessa propriedade também dimensionará os ornamentos do <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> e o <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-110">Use of this property will also scale the embellishments of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutLineAnchorCapStyle%2A> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.CalloutStyle%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="33f59-111">A movimentação de rótulos inteligentes pode ser controlada com o uso de várias propriedades relacionadas ao movimento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-111">The movement of smart labels can be controlled through the use of several motion-related properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-112">Elas definem as regras de movimentação para a direção, distância e se o ponto de dados rótulo é permitido para deixar a área de plotagem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-112">These define the rules of movement for the direction, distance and whether the data point label is allowed to leave the plotting area.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-113">As regras de movimentação padrão normalmente resolverá a maioria dos problemas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-113">The default movement rules will normally resolve most issues.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-114">O <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> define um valor que especifica a distância máxima em pixels a partir dos dados de ponto que os rótulos de ponto de dados podem ser movidos em caso de sobreposição.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-114">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> defines a value that specifies the maximum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels are allowed to be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-115">O <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> propriedade define um valor que especifica a distância mínima, em pixels a partir dos dados de ponto que os rótulos de ponto de dados serão movidos em caso de sobreposição.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-115">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> property defines a value that specifies the minimum distance in pixels from the data point that data point labels will be moved in case of overlapping.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-116">Quando um ponto de dados rótulo precisa ser reposicionado, o rótulo será movido pelo menos o número de pixels especificado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-116">When a data point label needs to be repositioned, the label will be moved by at least the number of pixels specified.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="33f59-117">O <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> propriedade indica se os rótulos estão ocultos quando problemas de sobreposição não podem ser resolvido.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-117">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property indicates whether the labels are hidden when overlapping issues cannot be resolved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-118">Se o <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> é de propriedade `true`, e o ponto de dados não pode ser desenhado dentro da área especificada por <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> e <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> nas direções permitidas pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, o rótulo de ponto de dados não será desenhado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-118">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.IsOverlappedHidden%2A> property is `true`, and the data point cannot be drawn within the area specified by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MinMovingDistance%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MaxMovingDistance%2A> in the directions allowed by <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A>, the data point label will not be drawn.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="33f59-119">O <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> propriedade define as direções em que o rótulo de ponto de dados pode ser movido.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-119">The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.SmartLabelStyle.MovingDirection%2A> property defines the direction(s) in which the data point label can be moved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-120">Essa propriedade aceita uma <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valor ou um bit a bit OR de vários <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valores.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-120">This property accepts one <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> value or a bitwise-OR of multiple <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33f59-121">O padrão é o bit a bit OR de todos os <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> valores, para permitir o reposicionamento em todas as direções possíveis, exceto para o Centro de dados de ponto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-121">The default is the bitwise-OR of all <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelAlignmentStyles> values, to allow repositioning in all possible directions except to the center of the data point.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="33f59-122">Não há suporte para rótulos inteligentes para os seguintes tipos de gráfico:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-122">Smart labels are not supported for the following chart types:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="33f59-123">Gráficos de barras: barras e gráficos de barras cem por cento empilhado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-123">Bar charts: bar and hundred-percent-stacked bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="33f59-124">Gráficos de forma: de pizza, rosca, polar e gráficos de radar.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-124">Shape charts: pie, doughnut, polar and radar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="33f59-125">Gráficos de intervalo: intervalo, a coluna de intervalo e gráficos de barras de intervalo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-125">Range charts: range, range column and range bar charts.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="33f59-126">Área gráficos empilhados: empilhada, área e gráficos de área de cem por cento empilhado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33f59-126">Stacked area charts: stacked area and hundred-percent-stacked area charts.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
Private Function SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
  
   ' Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.Enabled = true  
  
   ' Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined  
  
   ' Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   ' Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash  
  
   ' Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3   
  
   ' Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series("Series1").SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  
  
private void SetSmartLabelsOptions()  
{  
   // Enabling the SmartLabels™ attribute.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.Enabled = true;  
  
   // Set the callout style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutStyle = LabelCalloutStyle.Underlined;  
  
   // Set the callout line color.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineColor = Color.Goldenrod;  
  
   // Set the callout line style.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineStyle = ChartDashStyle.Dash;  
  
   // Set the callout line width.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineWidth = 3;  
  
   // Set the callout line anchor cap.  
   Chart1.Series["Series1"].SmartLabels.CalloutLineAnchorCap = LineAnchorCap.Arrow;  
}  
```
